description: This cluster provides a feature for the device to tag an endpoint with zero or more read only labels. Examples: • A bridge can use this to indicate grouping of bridged devices. For example: All bridged devices whose endpoints have an entry in their LabelList "room":"bedroom 2" are in the same (bed)room.
